d in molecular\ndynamics simulations of 2D non-additive disks, suggesting an efficient method\nfor describing confined systems with reduced dimensionality representations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2022 20:05:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 08:42:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2022 05:52:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 06:43:18 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 19 May 2023 02:25:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-22"}
